Katia Tchenko https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Katia_Tchenko 0 Katia Tchenko (born 8 May 1947) is a French actress. She has appeared in more than 100 films and television shows since 1967. In 1999 she was a member of the jury at the 21st Moscow International Film Festival. Katia_Tchenko ( born 8_May_1947 ) is a_French_actress .
